short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A plugin for recording web element locators

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Locators Finder is a Chrome extension designed to help users record web element locators effortlessly. The extension provides an intuitive interface for capturing locators, editing, and managing them, and supports copying locators in JSON format to the clipboard. This documentation will guide you through the installation, usage, and features of the extension.
